text: An insole is the inner sole of a shoe or other footwear. Insole may also refer to: * Doug Insole (1926–2017), English cricketer *George Insole (1790–1851), South Wales colliery owner *James Harvey Insole (1821–1901), South Wales colliery owner * Insole Court, a Victorian Gothic mansion in Cardiff, Wales
title: Insole (disambiguation)
